HEADWORD: airline
<hw>air"line`</hw>. <def>an organization, usually commercial or
governmental, providing transportation by airplane for freight or
passengers. The term includes the organization, its personnel, equipment
and other properties, such as approved air routes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC.</source>]</p>

